%%{init: {'theme': 'default'}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Start: gforms deploy] --> B[Load form definition]
    B --> C{Valid TypeScript?}
    C -->|No| D[Show validation errors]
    D --> E[Exit with error]

    C -->|Yes| F[Authenticate with Google]
    F --> G{Auth successful?}
    G -->|No| H[Show auth error]
    H --> E

    G -->|Yes| I[Check if form exists]
    I --> J{Form ID in state?}

    J -->|No| K[Mark as NEW form]
    J -->|Yes| L[Fetch remote form state]

    L --> M{Fetch successful?}
    M -->|No| N[Show network error]
    N --> E

    M -->|Yes| O[Calculate diff]
    K --> O

    O --> P{Changes detected?}
    P -->|No| Q[No changes to deploy]
    Q --> R[Exit success]

    P -->|Yes| S[Display diff]
    S --> T{--yes flag?}

    T -->|Yes| U[Proceed to deploy]
    T -->|No| V{User confirms?}

    V -->|No| W[Aborted by user]
    W --> R

    V -->|Yes| U

    U --> X[Apply form changes]
    X --> Y{Form updated?}
    Y -->|No| Z[Show API error]
    Z --> E

    Y -->|Yes| AA[Configure integrations]
    AA --> AB[Update state file]
    AB --> AC[Display URLs]
    AC --> R

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style R fill:#c8e6c9
    style E fill:#ffcdd2
